Hey, you can call me Tess; 

I love writing fan fiction and my requests are currently open! 

I love all things Opera, Avengers, Chilling Adventures of Sabrina, and a few random things here and there. My true loves are Chris Evans, Tom Holland and Gavin Leatherwood

Kimberly, 32, Panromantic Asexual, from VT, in love with Rami Malek...also neurodivergent and recently diagnosed with MS. so I guess I'm not just falling apart mentally anymore. my body has consistency, people
@ivebeenmade is the Ruby to my Sapphire, the Ward to my Fitz, the Scott to my Isaac, the Nicky to my Troy, the Howard to my Bucky, the Seth to my Donnie, the Steve to my tony, the Marceline to my Princess Bubblegum, the Rick to my Daryl, the Aaron to my Jesus, the Deadpool to my Spidey, the Eddie to my venom, the Tyrell to my Elliot, the Crowley to my Aziraphale...
And as for the blog, let me be honest, its mostly shit posting and fandom discourse. teen wolf/FTWD/BUCKY BARNES/TWD/sometimes AOS (except theyve all pretty much killed/ruined everything I love). you'll find some random shit thrown in here and there because I thought it was nifty or pretty. I love Iain De Caestecker, Brett Dalton, Daniel Sharman, Sebabstian Stan, Frank Dillane, Tom Payne, and everything they do so expect A LOT of their faces. Also, again, Bucky Barnes.
